//- index.pug
doctype html
html
  include includes/head.pug

  body
    h1 My Site
    p Welcome to my super lame site.
    ul
    for item in items
      li= item.name

    include includes/foot.pug
//- includes/head.pug
head
  meta(chaset="utf-8")
  title My Site

  script(type="javascript")
    include /js/items.js

  style(type="text/css")
    include /css/main.css
//- includes/foot.pug
footer#footer
  p Copyright (c) foobar
